Tin x l d liu ngi dng

Qu trnh tin x l c thc hin trn b d liu cresci-2015, tp trung vo cc thng tin lin quan n ti khon ngi dng. D liu c ly t hai ngun khc nhau, gm ti khon tht v ti khon gi mo (bot), sau c gp li thnh mt tp duy nht. Cc gi tr thiu c x l ph hp vi kiu d liu v d liu dng chui c m ha phc v cho vic hun luyn m hnh. Vic chn lc cc ct thng tin quan trng gip gim nhiu v tng hiu qu phn tch. Tp d liu sau x l s c s dng phn tch v xy dng m hnh pht hin ti khon gi mo.

Kt qu thu c l mt bng danh sch cnh hon chnh, ng vai tr l cu trc th u vo cho m hnh hc su trn th.

Chuyn i d liu thnh graph tensor

D liu ngi dng v cc kt ni bn b c chuyn i thnh mt cu trc th phc v cho hun luyn m hnh GNN. c trng ngi dng c trch xut t bng users, sau chuyn thnh tensor x. Danh sch cnh c biu din di dng tensor edge_index theo nh dng [2, num_edges], c thm self-loop tng tnh n nh trong qu trnh hun luyn. Nhn phn loi c ly t ct dataset, th hin ti khon tht hoc gi. Cui cng, tt c thnh phn c ng gi vo i tng Data ca th vin PyTorch Geometric, sn sng cho cc bc hun luyn m hnh hc su trn th.

In[4]:
# Chuyn i d liu ngi dng thnh tensor
x = users.drop(['id','dataset'], axis=1).values
x = torch.tensor(x, dtype=torch.float)

# Chuyn i d liu cnh thnh tensor v thm thm cc cnh t ni (self-loops)
edge_index = torch.tensor(edges[['source_index', 'target_index']].values, dtype=torch.long).t().contiguous()
edge_index, _ = add_self_loops(edge_index, num_nodes=x.size(0))

# Chuyn i nhn ngi dng thnh tensor
y = torch.tensor(users.dataset, dtype=torch.long)

# To i tng graph t d liu ngi dng, cc cnh v nhn
graph = Data(x=x, edge_index=edge_index, y=y)
display(graph)

Chia d liu v to mask cho hun luyn, xc thc v kim tra

D liu th c chia thnh ba tp: hun luyn, xc thc v kim tra theo t l 70/15/15. Vic chia gi nguyn phn b nhn gia cc tp m bo tnh cng bng trong nh gi. Cc tp c biu din bng cc mask boolean gm train_mask, val_mask v test_mask. Nhng mask ny c gn trc tip vo i tng graph. Vic phn chia r rng gip m hnh c hun luyn hiu qu v nh gi chnh xc hn.

In[6]:
# Chia d liu thnh tp hun luyn v tp kim tra
num_nodes = graph.num_nodes
labels = users.dataset.to_numpy()
train, temp = train_test_split(
    range(num_nodes),
    test_size=0.3, 
    random_state=42,
    stratify=labels
)
val, test = train_test_split(
    temp, 
    test_size=0.5, 
    random_state=42, 
    stratify=labels[temp]
)

# To mask cho tp hun luyn v tp kim tra
train_mask = torch.zeros(num_nodes, dtype=torch.bool)
val_mask = torch.zeros(num_nodes, dtype=torch.bool)
test_mask = torch.zeros(num_nodes, dtype=torch.bool)

# Gn gi tr True cho cc ch mc trong tp hun luyn v tp kim tra
train_mask[train] = True
val_mask[val] = True
test_mask[test] = True

# Gn cc mask vo i tng graph
graph.train_mask = train_mask
graph.val_mask = val_mask
graph.test_mask = test_mask
print(f"Train nodes: {graph.train_mask.sum()}, Val nodes: {graph.val_mask.sum()}, Test nodes: {graph.test_mask.sum()}")

Khi to m hnh GCN

Graph Convolutional Network (GCN) c xy dng bng th vin PyTorch Geometric vi kin trc gm hai lp tch chp (GCNConv). D liu u vo i qua lp tch chp u tin, sau p dng hm kch hot ReLU v dropout, trc khi chuyn tip n lp tch chp th hai a ra xc sut phn loi. Qu trnh lan truyn thng tin trn th c m t bng cng thc chun ha nh sau:

$$ H^{(l+1)} = \sigma\left( \tilde{D}^{-1/2} \tilde{A} \tilde{D}^{-1/2} H^{(l)} W^{(l)} \right) $$

Trong :

  • $H^{(l)}$: ma trn c trng (feature matrix) ti lp th $l$
  • $W^{(l)}$: ma trn trng s c hc ti lp $l$
  • $\sigma$: hm kch hot phi tuyn, thng l ReLU
  • $\tilde{A} = A + I$: ma trn k (adjacency matrix) thm self-loop
  • $\tilde{D}$: ma trn bc (degree matrix) tng ng vi $\tilde{A}$

M hnh c khi to vi s c trng u vo bng graph.num_node_features, s chiu n l 64, v u ra l s lp phn loi t nhn ca ngi dng. Sau khi khi to, m hnh GCN sn sng hun luyn nhm phn loi ti khon tht v gi trong th ngi dng.

In[7]:
# nh ngha m hnh GCN
class GCN(torch.nn.Module):
    # Phng thc khi to kin trc m hnh GCN
    def __init__(self, in_channels, hidden_channels, num_classes):
        super().__init__()
        self.conv1 = GCNConv(in_channels, hidden_channels)
        self.conv2 = GCNConv(hidden_channels, num_classes)
        
    # Phng thc forward  thc hin qu trnh lan truyn qua cc lp GCNConv
    def forward(self, x, edge_index):
        x = self.conv1(x, edge_index)
        x = F.relu(x)
        x = F.dropout(x, p=0.5, training=self.training)
        x = self.conv2(x, edge_index)
        return x

# Khi to m hnh GCN c th
model = GCN(graph.num_node_features, 64, len(np.unique(users.dataset)))
display(model)

GCN(
  (conv1): GCNConv(8, 64)
  (conv2): GCNConv(64, 2)
)

Hun luyn v nh gi m hnh

Qu trnh hun luyn m hnh bt u bng vic khi to b ti u ha Adam vi tc hc l 0.01 v h s regularization 5e-4 nhm hn ch overfitting. Hm train() thc hin forward pass trn tp train, tnh ton hm mt mt cross-entropy v cp nht trng s thng qua lan truyn ngc. Hm mt mt c nh ngha nh sau:

$$ \mathcal{L}_{\text{train}} = - \sum_{i \in \text{Train}} y_i \cdot \log(\hat{y}_i) $$

Trong khi , hm test() chuyn m hnh sang ch nh gi (eval()), d on nhn bng argmax, ri tnh chnh xc trn c tp hun luyn v kim tra. Cng thc chnh xc l:

$$ \text{Accuracy} = \frac{\text{S lng d on ng}}{\text{Tng s mu trong tp}} $$

Sau nhiu vng lp (epoch), m hnh dn hc c cch phn bit ti khon tht v gi da trn cu trc v c trng ca th ngi dng.

In[8]:
# Khi to b ti u ha Adam vi m hnh v cc tham s hc
optimizer = torch.optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=0.01, weight_decay=5e-4)
display(optimizer)

# Phng thc hun luyn m hnh
def train():
    model.train()
    optimizer.zero_grad()
    out = model(graph.x, graph.edge_index)
    loss = F.cross_entropy(out[graph.train_mask], graph.y[graph.train_mask])
    loss.backward()
    optimizer.step()
    return loss.item()

# Phng thc kim tra m hnh
def test():
    model.eval()
    with torch.no_grad():
        out = model(graph.x, graph.edge_index)
        pred = out.argmax(dim=1)
    accs = []
    for mask in [graph.train_mask, graph.val_mask, graph.test_mask]:
        correct = pred[mask] == graph.y[mask]
        acc = int(correct.sum()) / int(mask.sum())
        accs.append(acc)
    return accs

# Khi to DataFrame  lu lch s hun luyn
history = pd.DataFrame(columns=['epoch', 'loss', 'train_acc', 'val_acc', 'test_acc'])

# Khi to cc gi tr phc v lu kt qu ti u nht
best_val_acc = 0
patience = 50
counter = 0
best_model_state = None

# Hun luyn m hnh v lu lch s hun luyn
for epoch in range(1, 101):
    loss = train()
    train_acc, val_acc, test_acc = test()
    print(f'Epoch: {epoch:03d}, Loss: {loss:.4f}, Train Acc: {train_acc:.4f},  Val Acc: {val_acc:.4f}, Test Acc: {test_acc:.4f}')
    history.loc[len(history)] = {
        'epoch': epoch,
        'loss': loss,
        'train_acc': train_acc,
        'val_acc': val_acc,
        'test_acc': test_acc
    }
    if val_acc > best_val_acc:
        best_val_acc = val_acc
        counter = 0
        best_model_state = model.state_dict()
    else:
        counter += 1
    if counter >= patience:
        print(f"GCN Early stopped at epoch {epoch} with Val Acc = {best_val_acc:.4f}")
        break
    if epoch == 100:
        print(f"GCN stopped at epoch {epoch} with Val Acc = {best_val_acc:.4f}")

nh gi hiu sut m hnh

Sau khi hun luyn, m hnh c nh gi ton din thng qua nhiu ch s khc nhau. u tin l chnh xc tng th (Accuracy), c tnh bng t l phn trm s mu c phn loi ng:

$$ \text{Accuracy} = \frac{1}{N} \sum_{i=1}^N \mathbf{1}(y_i = \hat{y}_i) $$

Ngoi ra, ma trn nhm ln c s dng phn tch chi tit s lng d on ng/sai gia cc lp Real v Fake. Bo co phn loi (Classification Report) cung cp cc ch s quan trng gm Precision, Recall v F1-score:

$$ \text{Precision} = \frac{TP}{TP + FP}, \quad \text{Recall} = \frac{TP}{TP + FN}, \quad \text{F1-score} = 2 \cdot \frac{\text{Precision} \cdot \text{Recall}}{\text{Precision} + \text{Recall}} $$

Cui cng, biu ROC v ch s AUC phn nh kh nng phn bit hai lp ca m hnh, trong AUC c nh ngha l:

$$ \text{AUC} = \int_0^1 \text{TPR}(FPR) \, d(\text{FPR}) $$

Tp hp cc ch s nh lng ny gip nh gi ton din hiu sut ca m hnh trong vic phn loi ti khon tht v gi trn th ngi dng.

# Kim tra trn ton b d liu hun luyn
model.load_state_dict(best_model_state)
model.eval()
with torch.no_grad():
    out = model(graph.x, graph.edge_index)
    predictions = out.argmax(dim=1).numpy()
    acc = (predictions == graph.y.numpy()).sum() / graph.y.size(0)
    true_labels = graph.y.numpy()
    probs = out[:, 1].numpy()
cm = confusion_matrix(graph.y.numpy(), predictions)
roc_auc = roc_auc_score(true_labels, probs)
fpr, tpr, thresholds = roc_curve(true_labels, probs)

# Hin th cc ch s nh gi m hnh
print(classification_report(true_labels, predictions, target_names=["Real", "Fake"]))
